            . On the 14th of November, about eight o'clock in the evening, I was in <placeName id="t18221204-161-crimeloc831">Queen-street, Soho</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18221204-161-crimeloc831" type="placeName" value="Queen-street, Soho"></interp>
