                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18221204-161-off829 t18221204-161-crimeloc831"></join> - a man came up behind me, took off my hat, and ran off with it; I gave an alarm. I did not see who it was. He was followed and secured, but not in my sight.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18221204-161-person1394">
                  WILLIAM 
                  HALFPENNY
               <interp inst="t18221204-161-person1394" type="surname" value="HALFPENNY"></interp>
