                     <interp inst="t18221204-161-person1394" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was in Queen-street, heard the cry, and met the prisoner running with the hat in his hand at the corner of Frith-street - I collared him; he struggled, and got from me, turned the corner, and in Soho-square I saw him stopped again.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18221204-161-person1395">
                  CHARLES 
                  WILLIAM GREEN
               <interp inst="t18221204-161-person1395" type="surname" value="WILLIAM GREEN"></interp>
