                     <interp inst="t18221204-161-person1395" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I heard the cry; the prisoner ran up Frith-street very hard, and had something which he flung away. I stopped him; he said he was innocent. The last witness came up, and assisted in taking him back. A gentleman brought back the hat.</p>
